/>\n好明顯大家嘅感情係淡左<br />\n前幾日出街手都唔比拖 掂佢手一下即刻有副厭煩嘅神情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係送佢搭車返屋企個時先拖到一陣 但即刻又甩開我隻手<br />\n連我送佢上車我都係講大話話想上車訓一陣<br />\n因為我知佢唔想我送佢返去 可能係怕我攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家又冇話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然知佢返工攰 但我都想見下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成半個月先見一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係咪騎劫左你個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ac854b95199b15aac1d1b79ab9f3f88dd40f5e","tid":571081,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"眼淚在心裡流"},{"pid":"58fc2f2472779a0fedd67ffbec6124c99844e0d5","tid":571081,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e7d9fe9e283fa3df69520c66fe24b473b080b2","tid":571081,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩又扮左次無所謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"無所謂 佢都成日講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係無法子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e583b5e6ab44db313ab67f3aad3fcb8692b207c","tid":571081,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ac854b95199b15aac1d1b79ab9f3f88dd40f5e","tid":571081,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"眼淚在心裡流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"苦痛～問君知否"},{"pid":"0266402ac419d8089dc2fec0644cf24900fc86ac","tid":571081,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對唔住 係我錯<br />\n我唔應該話同你去旅行 結果講同返左工成年我個銀行仲係2000樓下<br />\n我唔應該成日chur你 搞到你覺得我好煩<br />\n我唔應該成日逼你斷社交 <br />\n我唔應該成日趁你有假個時先出去同朋友仔玩 雖然真係唔知 成日都係咁 <br />\n我唔應該比你覺得我仲好細個 好冇安全感<br />\n我根本就唔適合拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然未分手 但我覺得就近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想搵人傾訴 但我覺得冇一個係真正朋友<br />\n定係我只係唔想比朋友屌柒我<br />\nI dont know<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你知自己有咩做得唔夠好<br />\n如果你仲愛力 就趁未分手 未完全死心做返好佢 挽回返佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩想傾既就係到講啦</blockquote>儲左一筆錢4月底同佢去旅行<br />\n希望可以重拾愛火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好明顯大家嘅感情係淡左<br />\n前幾日出街手都唔比拖 掂佢手一下即刻有副厭煩嘅神情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係送佢搭車返屋企個時先拖到一陣 但即刻又甩開我隻手<br />\n連我送佢上車我都係講大話話想上車訓一陣<br />\n因為我知佢唔想我送佢返去 可能係怕我攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家又冇話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然知佢返工攰 但我都想見下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成半個月先見一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係咪騎劫左你個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可能係心淡 你要體諒佢而家會有咁既反應<br />\n好好同佢傾下 講對唔住同show俾佢睇你真係會改你以前唔好既野 <br />\n點解你地半個月先見一次既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f47541b61288372dff606d330699cc3e2a9ecd","tid":571081,"uid":147988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩又扮左次無所謂</blockquote>無所謂 佢都成日講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係無法子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解佢成日都講呀 <br />\n覺得每講一次無所謂個心都會傷一次咁<br />\n明明好想同你講其實自己唔開心 但怕你指責返我 唔想大家又因為咁既嘈 我就決定吞哂自己想講既野 扮善解人意扮無所謂咁就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463022d37a3f84f1ecafd435ab25895b3d4ba3bb","tid":571081,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0266402ac419d8089dc2fec0644cf24900fc86ac","tid":571081,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對唔住 係我錯<br />\n我唔應該話同你去旅行 結果講同返左工成年我個銀行仲係2000樓下<br />\n我唔應該成日chur你 搞到你覺得我好煩<br />\n我唔應該成日逼你斷社交 <br />\n我唔應該成日趁你有假個時先出去同朋友仔玩 雖然真係唔知 成日都係咁 <br />\n我唔應該比你覺得我仲好細個 好冇安全感<br />\n我根本就唔適合拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然未分手 但我覺得就近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想搵人傾訴 但我覺得冇一個係真正朋友<br />\n定係我只係唔想比朋友屌柒我<br />\nI dont know<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你知自己有咩做得唔夠好<br />\n如果你仲愛力 就趁未分手 未完全死心做返好佢 挽回返佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩想傾既就係到講啦</blockquote>儲左一筆錢4月底同佢去旅行<br />\n希望可以重拾愛火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好明顯大家嘅感情係淡左<br />\n前幾日出街手都唔比拖 掂佢手一下即刻有副厭煩嘅神情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係送佢搭車返屋企個時先拖到一陣 但即刻又甩開我隻手<br />\n連我送佢上車我都係講大話話想上車訓一陣<br />\n因為我知佢唔想我送佢返去 可能係怕我攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家又冇話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然知佢返工攰 但我都想見下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成半個月先見一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係咪騎劫左你個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可能係心淡 你要體諒佢而家會有咁既反應<br />\n好好同佢傾下 講對唔住同show俾佢睇你真係會改你以前唔好既野 <br />\n點解你地半個月先見一次既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"我返工返學 佢返工 大家假期唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80806e6a64701a836cdec32a82e1c525759439a5","tid":571081,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13f47541b61288372dff606d330699cc3e2a9ecd","tid":571081,"uid":147988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩又扮左次無所謂</blockquote>無所謂 佢都成日講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我真係無法子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解佢成日都講呀 <br />\n覺得每講一次無所謂個心都會傷一次咁<br />\n明明好想同你講其實自己唔開心 但怕你指責返我 唔想大家又因為咁既嘈 我就決定吞哂自己想講既野 扮善解人意扮無所謂咁就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:21:35.000Z","msg":"所以你男朋友會再接再勵的 不如你講實話 男人唔受過苦唔知痛㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咪成日就係講d唔會實現到嘅野出黎<br />\n到最後佢都話無所謂啦 都慣左/預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&